OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fcontinuing into the evening before
OL,7,Fgradually easing overnight with some
OL,8,Fareas becoming dry by dawn. A brisk
OL,9,Fbreeze continuing overnight, with
OL,10,Ftemperatures remaining on the mild
OL,11,Fside.
OL,12,
OL,13,CWednesday:FVariable cloud with bright
OL,14,Fspells and just isolated light
OL,15,Fshowers, A brisk breeze but feeling
OL,16,Fwarmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
