OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FThursday, cloudy start turning
OL,7,Fbrighter and warmer. Friday, sunny and
OL,8,Fvery warm, locally hot. Chance of
OL,9,Fthundery evening showers. Saturday,
OL,10,Fvery warm with bright spells, thundery
OL,11,Fshowers still possible.
